parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to hesitate or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates for 1-2 seconds before moving from a stop
the vehicle completely stops and won't drive while in "Drive" range
the "Slow Down" message displays on the instrument panel
the vehicle stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: AYC pump failure can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The AYC pump warning light comes on
the pump needs to be relocated and replaced
the pump fails while driving
causing a safety hazard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences a loss of power
increased exhaust noise
and the illumination of powertrain fault lights on the instrument cluster
the engine bay catches fire
the main relay catches fire and melts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Clutch failure can cause the vehicle to hesitate or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: An abnormal clicking sound emits from the vehicle when the clutch pedal is depressed
brake fluid leaks inside the vehicle onto the floorboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: CVT transmission failure can cause the vehicle to hesitate or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission will not move the car when the car and engine are cold
the car revs to 1500-2000 RPM and eventually begins to creep forward.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injury or fatalities, as the vehicle's safety features are compromised.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
warning indicators light up on the dashboard
seatbelt and airbag warning pictures appear on the display.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed or Unavailable Airbag Recall Repairs
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of airbag recall repairs can leave vehicles on the road with potentially faulty airbags, putting drivers and passengers at risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Notification of airbag recall
part not available for repair
manufacturer exceeds reasonable time for recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Overly aggressive airbag deployment can cause injuries, even in low-speed crashes, and may be particularly dangerous for vulnerable individuals, such as the elderly or those with pre-existing medical conditions.
symptoms: Airbag deploys with excessive force
causing pain or injury
prolonged recovery time from airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting and cracking of the subframe can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries.
symptoms: Rust or corrosion on the subframe
cracks or damage to the subframe
uneven tire wear
difficulty steering or handling the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags to deploy in a crash can increase the risk of injury or fatality to the occupants.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
vehicle fails to shut off engine after impact
lack of warning lights or indicators.
